t with decorative elements like flourishes or badges. High-quality, print-ready with sharp details and professional composition suitable for apparel or home decor. GPT Image Remix Image Image to Video Let me also create a flowchart showing the complete print-on-demand design optimization process: Using Tool | MCP Chart Server MCP: generate_flow_diagram {\"data\":{\"nodes\":[{\"name\":\"Original Image\"},{\"name\":\"Quality Assessment\"},{\"name\":\"Resolution Check\"},{\"name\":\"Color Analysis\"},{\"name\":\"Typography Review\"},{\"name\":\"AI Enhancement\"},{\"name\":\"Vector Recreation\"},{\"name\":\"Print Optimization\"},{\"name\":\"Format Export\"},{\"name\":\"Mockup Creation\"},{\"name\":\"Upload Ready\"}],\"edges\":[{\"source\":\"Original Image\",\"target\":\"Quality Assessment\",\"name\":\"Analyze\"},{\"source\":\"Quality Assessment\",\"target\":\"Resolution Check\",\"name\":\"Check DPI\"},{\"source\":\"Quality Assessment\",\"target\":\"Color Analysis\",\"name\":\"Review Colors\"},{\"source\":\"Quality Assessment\",\"target\":\"Typography Review\",\"name\":\"Check Text\"},{\"source\":\"Resolution Check\",\"target\":\"AI Enhancement\",\"name\":\"If Low Res\"},{\"source\":\"Color Analysis\",\"target\":\"Print Optimization\",\"name\":\"CMYK Convert\"},{\"source\":\"Typography Review\",\"target\":\"Vector Recreation\",\"name\":\"If Pixelated\"},{\"source\":\"AI Enhancement\",\"target\":\"Print Optimization\",\"name\":\"Enhanced\"},{\"source\":\"Vector Recreation\",\"target\":\"Print Optimization\",\"name\":\"Vector Text\"},{\"source\":\"Print Optimization\",\"target\":\"Format Export\",\"name\":\"Optimize\"},{\"source\":\"Format Export\",\"target\":\"Mockup Creation\",\"name\":\"Multiple Formats\"},{\"source\":\"Mockup Creation\",\"target\":\"Upload Ready\",\"name\":\"Final Review\"}]}} View PROFESSIONAL PRINT-ON-DEMAND TRANSFORMATION STRATEGY Here are your design examples and the complete optimization framework: DETAILED IMPLEMENTATION ROADMAP Phase 1: Quality 