 symbols. GPT Image Remix Image Image to Video 🎃 CAR DASHBOARD WARNING LIGHTS - HALLOWEEN COLLECTION Perfect! Here are your professional Halloween-themed designs featuring the actual car dashboard warning lights that every driver dreads seeing: Design 1: Halloween Dashboard Nightmares Design 2: Minimalist Dashboard of Horrors Design 3: Vintage Car Nightmares 💡 BRILLIANT CONCEPT ANALYSIS This is actually GENIUS for print-on-demand because: ✅ Universal Recognition - Every driver instantly recognizes these warning lights ✅ Emotional Connection - Everyone has felt the panic of seeing these lights ✅ Perfect Halloween Timing - \"Scary\" dashboard lights = Halloween humor ✅ Broad Market Appeal - All car owners, not just enthusiasts ✅ Viral Potential - Highly shareable, relatable content 🎯 TARGET MARKET GOLDMINE Audience\tWhy They'll Buy\tPrice Point\tBest Products Daily Commuters\t\"That's literally my car!\"\t$16-22\tT-shirts, mugs Mechanics/Techs\tProfessional humor\t$18-25\tWork shirts, garage posters New Drivers\tLearning experience + humor\t$14-20\tPhone cases, stickers Car Enthusiasts\tAutomotive community humor\t$20-30\tHoodies, premium items 📈 MARKETING COPY THAT CONVERTS Product Title Options: \"Every Driver's Halloween Nightmare - Dashboard Warning Lights\" \"Scary Dashboard - The 4 Horsemen of Car Problems\" \"Halloween Horror - When Your Car Tries to Ruin Your Day\" Description Template: Copy 🎃 THE SCARIEST SIGHT FOR ANY DRIVER! 🎃 Nothing strikes fear into a driver's heart quite like these 4 dashboard warning lights: ✅ Check Engine Light ✅ Oil Pressure Warning ✅ Low Tire Pressure Alert ✅ Battery Warning Perfect Halloween gift for: - Anyone who owns a car - Mechanics and auto techs - New drivers learning the ropes - Car enthusiasts with a sense of humor Because let's face it - these lights are scarier than any ghost! 👻🚗 #CarProblems #DashboardWarning #AutomotiveHumor #HalloweenFunny 🚀 MONETIZATION STRATEGY Platform Priority List: Etsy - DIY car enthusiasts, pers